data.description: Experience serenity and accessibility in this charmingly renovated ranch-style home. Nestled on 6.3 acres of land, this residence seamlessly blends privacy with urban conveniences. Step inside to discover a spacious and luminous layout, crafted for effortless single-level living. The expansive kitchen boasts newly installed LPV flooring, sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinetry. Retreat to the primary bedroom, complete with a sizable walk-in closet and a luxurious spa-inspired ensuite. Across the home, two additional bedrooms await, one with direct access to a full bath. Step onto the deck and indulge in the natural splendor that surrounds you. With 6.3 acres to explore, you can sculpt your outdoor oasis, whether it's cultivating gardens, housing chickens, accommodating horses, or carving ATV trails. Unleash your outdoor aspirations and seize the opportunity to call this extraordinary property your own. Additionally, an RV hookup is available for added convenience.
